<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉啊，難得你來找我玩，<delay20 />
但我身體卻不太舒服。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我吃了
<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />給我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />之後，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺已經好不少了喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天<delay8 />真的很謝謝你來探病啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛<delay8 />已經吃下<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />給我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />了，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接下來就是<delay8 />靠氣勢跟毅力搞定啦──！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay8 />真是抱歉啊！<delay20 />
