所以我現在已經完全康復囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子<delay8 />讓你看到我病懨懨的樣子，<delay20 />
