<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧了<tag a="115" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />送我的<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
我現在身體跟肌肉的狀況<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都非常萬全喔！</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />老實說<delay8 />一直到剛才，
