<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的病一下就痊癒啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天身體很不舒服，<delay8 />
