<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在我已經完全康復了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我前陣子<delay8 />不小心得了感冒，<delay8 />
