	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你剛才<delay8 />送<colour id="1" />藥<colour id="65535" />給我啊！<delay frames="30" />
